desc_short	-----								CounterAttack is a side scrolling space shooter (shmup). Team up or fight solo, 1 - 2 player local or up to 4 players online coop, unlock upgrades, use powerful ultimate abilities, enhance your ship the way you want, and save the Earth from annihilation.							
